Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:03.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to protect the purity of the 4.5 tatami room,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don iron armor when venturing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:09.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Armed by theory, sophistries at the ready, \Nwith a brazen, soft-coated, nonchalant smile,
