Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:30.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my studies, exercise, popularity, good looks, all left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:34.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lie here, completely removed from those crucial pillars, stark naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish I could go back in time to that day!
