Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A convenience store onigiri would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it were cold and hardened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd trade 1,000 fish burgers for 1 onigiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a bowl of fresh cooked rice were placed before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am sure tears would flood down from my eyes in torrents!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what I truly yearn for is Neko Ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:30.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A world where I can go eat at Neko Ramen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,setting up shop randomly in the middle of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:31.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That world is what I'd call...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,...paradise.
