Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs160.594796\be1\bord0\c&H000000&\fnCalisto MT}Ozu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who brought a \NCastella to most of my rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Participating in many circles, \NI still don't have a full portrait of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the info I have, \Nhe would get in the way of people's love,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,setting off fires and scenes of carnage on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the disciple of Master Higuchi he \Ncreated an exposé film on Mr. Jougasaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,all the while sucking up to Mr. Jougasaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:56.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and as a double agent dyeing Mr. Higuchi's yukata pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before long as a tool of Aijima he \Nwas kicked out of the movie circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:03.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and this time entrapping Aijima, he climbed his way to the top of the Secret Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:06.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bulletin board was also Ozu's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,While extolling the joys of the \NRenaissance man-like campus life,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,he continued to meddle in every one of my lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had only met him, then I bet my campus life would have been a fun one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu always seemed to be my only real friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:44.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was Ozu's smartphone that he must have forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:49.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried all kinds of passwords, then for fun \NI punched in Kohinata-san's name and it unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:52.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazingly, it seems that \NKohinata-san was Ozu's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:52.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:55.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he ever introduce her to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seemed like this was Ozu's big secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:03.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu asked to borrow the airship that Honwaka had, but he was told no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were tossed around in the crowd of people, \Nand she ended up crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, I can't just... So suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ceremonial fires of Gozan are \Na symbol of the summer nights of Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the fives mountains surrounding the basin,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:20.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Daimonji," "Myouho," "The Ship," the left "Daimonji," and "The Gate" are each lit up in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is impossible to see them all from the ground at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ozu planned on going on a sightseeing flight to see the Gozan with Kohinata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\an8\p1\c&HFCFCFC&\move(701.461378,300.111524,701.461378,0)}m 282 146 l 1639 150 1641 393 949 385 947 505 1643 495 1639 616 286 618 290 865 1635 853 1637 734 288 740
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fscx95\fs99.36803\be2\c&H070707&\move(310.647182,469.739777,310.647182,169.628253)}Wait for me in the top bell tower \Nof the Honwaka Health Facility \Nat 19:50. \N\NI'll come to pick you up in an airship. \N\N\NKeep it a secret from your father and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed like Ozu planned on taking the airship by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just borrowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a fearfully pure love. \NAn idiot through and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where he gets all that boldness from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really the judgment of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,a human whose heart is so twisted they are mistaken for a youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're collecting information on this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gozan. Airship. Kohinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's heading right into Aijima's clutches!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:09:01.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an7\be2\c&H070707&\fs99.36803\fscx95\bord0\pos(282.588727,723.680297)}Aijima knows about your plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:09:01.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an7\be2\c&H070707&\fs99.36803\2a&HFF&\fscx95\bord0\pos(282.588727,844.126394)}{\k16}W{\k16}a{\k16}t{\k16}c{\k16}h{\k16} {\k16}o{\k16}u{\k16}t{\k16}!{\k16} {\k16}G{\k16}o{\k16}z{\k16}a{\k16}n{\k16} {\k16}i{\k16}s{\k16}n{\k16}'{\k16}t
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\p1\be2\c&HEEEEEE&\pos(375.782881,-3.011152)}m 601 481 l 823 494 1090 494 1354 473 1350 598 607 596
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be2\fscx95\fs110.408922\b0\c&H070707&\bord0\pos(960,478.773234)}Please charge
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:10.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gozan was more than 2 months after the day I became lost in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I could escape from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd eat the tarako spaghetti at Café Collection, \NI'd slurp Neko Ramen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd dive into the large tub at the public bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd go see movies at Kawaramachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd haggle with the old bookstore owner on Gabino,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd even listen during lectures at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd become Master Higuchi's disciple and engage in lewd storytelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd experience Hanuki-san's endless night of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd help Mr. Jougasaki with his passionate, meaningless films,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd even try dabbling in the secret society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:45.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though I tried lying to myself as consolation, it became harder and harder every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs120.446097\fnhomework smart\b0\be2\c&H303030&}Lavatory
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the room I originally lived in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, after these how many tens of days,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:04.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had returned to the 4.5 tatami room I started at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the corner of an \Nendless world of 4.5 tatami rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believed so strongly I was traveling through was in fact a small loop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the end of the world? Am I dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish I could live happily together with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:19.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had thought the days were all wasted, but they were such a bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always dreaming of the unrealistic, \NI never looked at what I had right around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the life I chose. \NAnd this is the result I wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was early evening at the Shimogamo used book fair the previous summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only a short stretch from my boarding house,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would go there every day, fishing for books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each one is a "Mochiguma."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:12.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All five as a group are called the "Mochiguman," but I have lost one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that point her expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,which was like some European fortress city, \Nrelaxed into a smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that smile made an impression that has never left my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:27.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, frankly, to put it plainly, honestly, saying it without any reservation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I fell head over heels for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That night, when I went to collect my clothes from the laundromat, mysteriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,my charcoal-colored boxers I had lovingly worn the past two years
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,had been switched with this little stuffed fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:47.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And although I put it in my pocket intending to give it to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:52.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should have thought to look for her, but I never took the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:58.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop wandering aimlessly, \Nand grab that opportunity with all your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take that step now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:04.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether it takes 100 steps, or 1,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu, have you no shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got nowhere to run, Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-senpai, have you done some more mischief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:56.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you say you're going to do \Nsomething to me, then I'm jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not coming down until you can guarantee my safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think you're in a position to bargain for your safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think about what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough! I'm jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:41.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu! Ozu! Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me! I'll cover for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moths!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the Kyoto newspaper the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the sudden outbreak of moths is still not properly understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I suspect you dear viewers understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He actually fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:02.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we kill him instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the type of guy who wouldn't stay down even if you killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:08.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow! My leg is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you go, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you care about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:17.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and I are connected by the black thread of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:24.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu is not going to run away, so calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ended up falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:36.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I said to "break a leg" for a girl, \NI didn't mean for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one incorrigible fool, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:39.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You reap what you sow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What nerve you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Jougasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you also a resident of Shimogamo Yuusuisou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave Ozu to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cover yourself with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't go by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanuki-san is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show her you're a man! Tell her "Come with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:15.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're an interesting person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having failed to steal the airship,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,he changed into women's clothes at the suggestion of Master Higuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and returned to Shimogamo \Ndown the canals of Lake Biwa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,where he was supposed to \Nrendezvous with the Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the disguise was easily seen through, or rather made him stand out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was cornered by Honwaka, \Nand members of the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,plus Mr. Jougasaki who had realized the betrayal of his disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,plus all manner of people whose love he had gotten in the way of,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,until he was forced onto the railing of the Kamo-oohashi and fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something I once picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it is yours, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:56.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you be the owner of the mouse-colored boxers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:18:01.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A year ago when I washed the Mochiguma, it got switched with some men's underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I've been searching for their owner ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that pair of underwear will fit me perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we go to Neko Ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:19.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason I have a feeling like I've \Nbeen waiting for those words for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it really that delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This flavor really is unmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it is not the purpose of this program
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,to show the further development of my relationship with Akashi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will refrain from showing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to throw my dear viewers' time down the gutter, now would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:43.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing else is as boring to tell as a story of successful love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was half forced to become Master Higuchi's disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the master has now disappeared on his journey around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\p1\be2\bord0\alpha&H80&\fscx613\fscy410\pos(960,748.773234)}m 0 0 l 0 25 l 230 25 l 230 0
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H120D0B&\fs76.282528\bord0\be2\fnVeteran Typewriter\pos(960,763.828996)}Do not try this with normal scrub brush
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:06.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My regret for becoming his disciple was some of the fastest in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but as I pulled the pins out from the globe,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:11.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I became entranced imagining where Master Higuchi must be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jougasaki said he left the laboratory and planned to get a job somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I wonder where the wordless beauty "Kaori-san" is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:22.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pray that Mr. Jougasaki and she are \Nleading a happy life together somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one thing Master Higuchi worried about,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:27.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the "Masochistic Proxy-Proxy War," was carried on by Ozu and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:33.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was in the hospital, I painted the bicycle he called "Dark Scorpion" pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:36.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To go along with the great change in myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:39.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a new boarding house in Motoanaka, and moved there with all haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:43.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I never wanted to spend the night in that 4.5 tatami room ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:46.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time I chose a 6 tatami room and made sure it had its own bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-san has a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't let that one go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:02.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stole the airship in order to let her see the bonfires from the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even called you all to the Kamo-oohashi to show how gallant he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. But he failed, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:12.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-san really hates it when the conversation turns to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:16.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he turns into a good boy when he's in front of his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the gang's all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:26.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even with all that evil you did, you still had time to go out with Kohinata-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What might you be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that you once called Hanuki-san for advice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,when you thought you were \Nbeing dumped, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lies! It's all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:39.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell us all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I invoke my right to remain silent! I want a lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a tough time even while you're in the hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:52.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you run away \Nsomewhere until things cool down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave the expenses to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you plotting? You can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should try trusting in other people more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are big-hearted people like me in this world, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In exchange, let me meet your girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! I refuse! You're so evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine then! It's all for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:15.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why must you be so interested in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the way I show my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can keep that icky love to yourself!
